      "text": "Devilish (デビリッシュ, Debirisshu) is an action video game that was released for the Game Gear.\nA sequel for the Mega Drive was released as Devilish: The Next Possession, known in Japan as Bad Omen (バッドオーメン, Baddo Ōmen). A third title in the series known as Devilish: Ball Bounder was released for Nintendo DS in 2005.",
